title: Liptov has it all: Sea, forgotten town and crooked peak
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
The Liptov region is a great holiday destination that is not just about Tatralandia, Jasná and Vlkolínec, although they are also worth a visit. 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec 
Guests: Linda Šimunová, Zuzana Trnovská, Gerdi Vanfleteren
